Bat Probe::

Some one in BLackFortress used a Bat-probe to send a message, in that 
way that anyone else could find out where the probe is or who sent 
the message. Message said: We're interested to enter to IGL's league, 
send to this frecuency rules and stuff like that in order to take the 
last decition about.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., KSLawdogg@c... wrote:
> Various Otyebis Crew:
> 
> 
> 
> 
> Dragoon's transmission was received by one of the many antennaes 
and was 
> processed.  Scans reported that the transmission had been reported 
from a 
> base that, according to the bounty hunters, belonged to a faction 
called the 
> Destrons ruled by Magmatron.  But they wanted to be sure.
> 
> A reply transmission was sent.  "Thank you, Dragoon, for entering 
the IGL's 
> Regular League.  We still need to know if you are in a faction, and 
if so 
> what is it called.  Thank you again."
